  "texts": [
    "Also, compared to traditional machine learning algorithms like SVM and MLP, deeplearning-based methods show a better performance in the early prediction of at-risk students.",
    "Figure 6 depicts the test accuracy values of different learning periods of APP-DGNN, AP-GT, and GRU.",
    "It is evident from the increasing prediction accuracies over time for APP-DGNN, AP-GT, and GRU that more academic information becomes available as the course progresses to enhance prediction precision.",
    "Specifically, as depicted in Fig. 6a, by the course's twentieth week, the proposed APP-DGNN achieves an accuracy 80.50% for predicting students at risk of failing.",
    "Moreover, it attains an accuracy 82.10% for predicting students at risk of dropping out, as shown in Fig. 6b."
